# .gitignore para Ada - Proyecto GPT

# --- OS Metadata (Linux/Universal) ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.directory
*.swp
*~

# --- IDEs & Editors (VS Code / Cursor / JetBrains) ---
.vscode/
.cursor/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Herramientas de Diseño ---
